PrecisApproval of a By-law No. 75 made by the MISTISSINI BAND on April 11, 1995 which changes the English, French and Cree names of this Band to "Cree Nation of Mistissini ", "la Nation Crie de Mistissini" and Mistissinii Iinuuch respectively.

precis:
Approval of a By-law No. 75 made by the MISTISSINI BAND on April 11, 1995
which changes the English, French and Cree names of this Band to "Cree
Nation of Mistissini ", "la Nation Crie de Mistissini" and Mistissinii
Iinuuch respectively.
